47
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:16,439
混蛋师徒 -> Dasar murid dan guru sialan.

48
00:06:17,840 --> 00:06:19,239
还没完 -> Tidak habisnya?

49
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:40,319
地球的价值不可估量 -> Nilai bumi tidak terhingga.

50
00:06:40,560 --> 00:06:44,399
